<br>
I've been quad kiting the spectres in OOT from 44 and I was just doing my second quad of 46 and I pull a gargoyle, not a problem - done it before, rooted it and continued to quad. I pull another gargoyle, no problem, same thing.<br>
<br>
I finish off 3/4 spectres and try to melee the last one to death, well root breaks and I run away a bit to re-root, I pull another gargoyle in the process and have 0 mana from the roots, I end up running around trying to swing past the spectre and throwing swings at it in order to kill it, it had 9% health when I was melee'ing with it and as I proceeded to run around it regained 11% HP, then ensnare breaks and for some reason it starts to chase me.<br>
<br>
Only way out is to swim to a level 51 warrior on the AC island, i'd be in the water too long and get killed if I swam directly there so I go to the Oracle island and then to the sister isle, when I get to the sister isle though, just as i'm doubling back to drop the gargoyles behind me a bit, the spectre life taps me and I reduce to the death walk, I essentially give up at this point and just take it from behind.<br>
<br>
I haven't died since level 40 when I was quadding in iceclad and Lodizal decided he didn't like me, why do I have to die in level 46? I dropped back to 45 and now have to spend another hour getting the exp back - I know thats not much time compared to higher levels but its still more than I could do with.<br>
<br>
Level 46 was what I got my last druid to before I deleted it out of agrovation, and if I die again during this level then i'm going to permanently stop playing EQ and encourage as many people as I can to play DAoC.<br>
<br>
This is the rant board, i'm allowed to rant!<br>
<br>
Serberus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unyssarainwhisper.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nyssa Rainwhisper</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://arnemetia.homestead.com/files/MiscImages/bluepawbullet.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(11/24/01 2:19:52 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://arnemetia.homestead.com/files/DAoC/lynxhead.jpg WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=116></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Death</span><hr size=1> Sorry you lost your lvl Serberus.<br>
